The paper deals with the problem of image retrieval and annotation, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The proposed method is based on a convolutional neural network (CNN), which is a popular technique in computer vision and deep learning. The paper also discusses the use of linear predictors and optimization techniques, which are relevant to information retrieval (cs.IR) and multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper deals with the problem of incomplete tags, which is a common issue in natural language processing (cs.CL).
